Data (data/events_impaired_circle.parquet, data/metrics_table.csv,
data/meeting_summary.csv)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Derived from the public dataset:

  "Heterogeneous UAV dataset for relative localization and cooperative flight"
  Václav Pritzl, Matouš Vrba, Petr Štěpán, Martin Saska (CTU-MRS), 2023.
  arXiv:2306.17544 — https://arxiv.org/abs/2306.17544

The data/ files contain (a) derived timing metadata for the recorded events and
(b) the OUTPUT of the MetricChrono engine on that public recording (corrected
timestamps and alignment errors). They do NOT contain the original dataset's raw
sensor payloads (images, point clouds). Synthetic impairment is seeded (424242).

Chrono-Metrics claims NO copyright over the underlying CTU-MRS recording; the derived
metadata and corrections are released for free reuse. If you redistribute, honor the
upstream CTU-MRS dataset's terms and cite arXiv:2306.17544. See DATA-LICENSE.md.

The MetricChrono engine that produced the corrections is proprietary and is NOT
included in this repository. The Apache-2.0 open core (the comparator/ladder
primitive) is at https://github.com/chrono-metrics/metricchrono.
